examples.en: He was overflowing with good ideas.
My heart was overflowing with gratitude.
He was a man of overflowing creativity.
Hospitals were reported to be overflowing with dead and wounded.
The house was full and people were overflowing into the street.
The house was overflowing with a profusion of strange ornaments.
Water from the overflowing bathtub inundated the bathroom floor.
